eu.trentorise.opendata.jackan.model

Class CkanGroup

  • java.lang.Object
    • eu.trentorise.opendata.jackan.model.CkanGroupOrgBase
      • eu.trentorise.opendata.jackan.model.CkanGroupOrg
        • eu.trentorise.opendata.jackan.model.CkanGroup

  • public class CkanGroup
extends CkanGroupOrg
    Class to explicitly model a Ckan group, which is not an organization, although it has the same attributes. CkanGroupOrgBase holds fields that can be sent when creating a group/organization, while CkanGroupOrg holds more fields that can be returned with searches. This class initializes nothing to fully preserve all we get from ckan. In practice, all fields of retrieved resources can be null except maybe name.
    Author:
    David Leoni
